(2, 2, '2010-11-15 11:16:57', '2010-11-15 11:16:57', '[caption id=\"attachment_277\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"264\" caption=\"<a href=\'http://www.madebysplendid.com/journal/article/lightbulb_sessions\' >Lightbulb Sessions</a> at 15 Queen St.\"]<a href=\"http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/files/2010/11/Lightbulb-Session.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-277\" title=\"Lightbulb-Session\" src=\"http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/files/2010/11/Lightbulb-Session-264x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"300\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nHello, I am a British graphic media student, currently in my final year of study. My main interests revolve around the careful construction of colours, letterforms and pixels. I like to design objects that are folded and pressed, but I also partake in my fair share of tag and query writing too. I am a self-confessed geek and have a passion for an open, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Network_neutrality\">neutral</a> internet, <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2010/nov/11/google-vint-cerf-internet?INTCMP=SRCH\">bursting</a> with <a href=\"http://data.gov.uk/\">data</a> and <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OM6XIICm_qo\">possibilities</a>.\r\n\r\nAs a designer, I take great pride in the expert treatment of typography and imagery. I feel that refining these points makes all the difference to a project.\r\n\r\nThis website has been lovingly coded using HTML, CSS, PHP and a pinch of JavaScript. Powered by <a href=\"http://www.wordpress.org/\">WordPress</a>, the framework of the layout is the great descendant of a <a href=\"http://wpshower.com/\">Wpshower</a> theme. The other designs and content however are proudly my own.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Aaron', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2011-04-07 15:27:49', '2011-04-07 15:27:49', '', 0, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(153, 2, '2009-08-03 19:12:59', '2009-08-03 19:12:59', 'ByDesign is a company that specialises in providing high quality office and leisure furniture to wide range of corporate clients. The site includes current stock of approved manufactures, as well as a list of previous clients, contact information and order forms. \r\n\r\nThe brief was to design a website that was easy to navigate and would give the company an online presence. \r\n', 'ByDesign', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bydesign', '', '', '2011-03-16 17:35:23', '2011-03-16 17:35:23', '', 0, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/?post_type=portfolio&p=153', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
