(102, 2, '2010-06-01 14:51:37', '2010-06-01 14:51:37', 'A second year project based on the guardians list of ‘The Greatest Speeches of the Twentieth Centuries’. I was asked to design a format in which to present the speeches in their entirety. The list includes fourteen of the most world changing speeches, the speakers of which include Winston Churchill, John F Kennedy and Martin Luther King.\r\n\r\nI decided to use a concertina fold to create a book of the manuscript of each, bound to two hard covers. The title and speaker of each was then screen printed on.', 'Great Speeches', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'great-speaches', '', '', '2011-06-29 18:46:29', '2011-06-29 18:46:29', '', 0, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/?post_type=portfolio&p=102', 0, 'portfolio', '', 0),
