(194, 1, '2010-12-11 17:07:57', '2010-12-11 17:07:57', 'My entry for Junes Lakota flyer competition. The brief was to design the artwork for a promotional leaflet to advertise upcoming events. \n\nMy original idea was to produce a clean a simple design which used a subtle palette, but ofter some consideration I decided that this style did not complement the Lakota brand. My second design (cocktail), I felt was better adapted to the brief and demanded the attention of the viewer more.', 'Lakota', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-autosave', '', '', '2010-12-11 17:07:57', '2010-12-11 17:07:57', '', 119, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/119-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
