(295, 1, '2011-03-18 23:29:38', '2011-03-18 23:29:38', '[caption id=\"attachment_128\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"264\" caption=\'<a href=\"http://www.madebysplendid.com/journal/article/lightbulb_sessions\">Lightbulb Session</a> at <a href=\"http://www.15queenstreet.org/\">15 Queen St.</a>\']<a href=\"http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/files/2010/11/portrait.jpg\"></a><a href=\"http://madebysplendid.com/journal/article/lightbulb_sessions\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-277\" title=\"Lightbulb-Session\" src=\"http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/files/2010/11/Lightbulb-Session-264x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"264\" height=\"300\" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nHello, I am a British graphic media student, currently in my final year of study. My main interests revolve around the careful construction of colours, letterforms and pixels.\r\n\r\nI like to design objects that are folded and pressed, but I also partake in my fair share  of tag and query writing too. I am a self-confessed geek and have a passion for an open, <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Network_neutrality\">neutral</a> internet, <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2010/nov/11/google-vint-cerf-internet?INTCMP=SRCH\">bursting</a> with <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://data.gov.uk/\">data</a> and <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OM6XIICm_qo\">possibilities</a>.\r\n\r\nAs a designer, I take great pride in the expert treatment of typography and imagery. I feel that refining these points makes all the difference to a project.\r\n\r\nThis website has been lovingly coded using HTML, CSS, PHP and a pinch of JavaScript. Powered by <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://www.wordpress.org\">WordPress</a>, the framework of the layout is the great descendant of a <a class=\"bodylink\" href=\"http://wpshower.com/\">Wpshower</a> theme. The other designs and content however are proudly my own.', 'Aaron', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision