(244, 1, '2011-03-22 11:29:16', '2011-03-22 11:29:16', 'A second year project, the brief was to design a series of artwork using found imagery from the sixties. The final works were to consist of a range of screen prints and a hand bound book. I decided to focus on the social unrest in france in the 1960’s, particularly the the student riots of 1968. \n\nFor the posters, I used a mix of amateur and journalistic photography and combined it with street art used throughout the protests. A digital version of the book can be found <a href=\"http://issuu.com/Aaronroot/docs/guidedwalks_final?mode=embed&layout=http%3A%2F%2Fskin.issuu.com%2Fv%2Flight%2Flayout.xml&showFlipBtn=true\" class=\"link\">here.</a>', 'Paris 1968', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '107-autosave', '', '', '2011-03-22 11:29:16', '2011-03-22 11:29:16', '', 107, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/107-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
