(249, 1, '2010-12-17 19:51:48', '2010-12-17 19:51:48', 'A second year project based on the guardians list of ‘The Greatest Speeches of the Twentieth Centuries’. I was asked to design a format in which to present the speeches in their entirety. The list includes fourteen of the most world changing speeches, the speakers of which include Winston Churchill, John F Kennedy and Martin Luther King.\n\nI decided to use a concertina fold to create a book of the manuscript of each, bound to two hard covers. The title and speaker of each was then screen printed on.', 'Great Speaches', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '102-autosave', '', '', '2010-12-17 19:51:48', '2010-12-17 19:51:48', '', 102, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/102-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
