(363, 1, '2011-05-06 20:26:22', '2011-05-06 20:26:22', 'Hello, I am a British graphic media student, currently in my final year of study. My main interests revolve around the careful construction of colours, letterforms and pixels. I like to design objects that are folded and pressed, but I also partake in my fair share of tag and query writing too. I am a self-confessed geek and have a passion for an open, neutral internet, bursting with data and possibilities.\r\n\r\nAs a designer, I take great pride in the expert treatment of typography and imagery. I feel that refining these points makes all the difference to a project.\r\n\r\nThis website has been lovingly coded using HTML, CSS, PHP and a pinch of JavaScript. Powered by WordPress, the framework of the layout is the great descendant of a Wpshower theme. The other designs and content however are proudly my own.', 'Sorry', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sorry', '', '', '2011-05-06 20:26:44', '2011-05-06 20:26:44', '', 0, 'http://www.adroot.co.uk/portfolio/?page_id=363', 0, 'page', '', 0),
