. <a href=\"http://xtreme-theme.com/\">Xtreme Theme</a></p><p><a href=\"http://crowdfavorite.com/\">Crowd Favorite</a> vs. <a href=\"http://workingwireframes.com/\">Working Wireframes</a></td><td class=\"column-5\"><a href=\"http://themejam.com/\">ThemeJam</a> vs. <a href=\"http://wpstartbox.com/\">Startbox</a></p><p><a href=\"http://prothemedesign.com/\">Pro Theme Design</a> vs. <a href=\"http://themeskingdom.com/\">Themes Kingdom</a></td></tr><tr class=\"row-4 even\"><td class=\"column-1\">April 13</td><td class=\"column-2\"><a href=\"http://themify.me/\">Themify</a> vs. <a href=\"http://bizzthemes.com/\">Bizz Themes</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.elegantthemes.com/\">Elegant Themes</a> vs. <a href=\"http://themetrust.com/\">Theme Trust</a></td><td class=\"column-3\"><a href=\"http://www.mojo-themes.com/\">Mojo Themes</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.theme-junkie.com/\">Theme Junkie</a></p><p><a href=\"http://templatic.com/\">Templatic</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.chimerathemes.com/\">ChimeraThemes</a></td><td class=\"column-4\"><a href=\"http://www.wpbundle.com/\">WPBundle</a> vs. <a href=\"http://catalysttheme.com/\">Catalyst Theme</a></p><p><a href=\"http://headwaythemes.com/\">Headway Themes</a> vs. <a href=\"http://alohathemes.com/\">Aloha Themes</a></td><td class=\"column-5\"><a href=\"http://www.kreativethemes.com/\">KreativeThemes</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.dessign.net/\">Dessign</a></p><p><a href=\"http://press75.com/\">Press75</a> vs. <a href=\"http://themes.bavotasan.com/\">Themes by Bavotasan</a></td></tr><tr class=\"row-5 odd\"><td class=\"column-1\">April 14</td><td class=\"column-2\"><a href=\"http://www.dev4press.com/\">Dev4Press</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.indonez.com/\">Indonez</a></p><p><a href=\"http://ithemes.com/\">iThemes</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.themewarrior.com/\">ThemeWarrior</a></td><td class=\"column-3\"><a href=\"http://www.wpzoom.com/\">WPZoom</a> vs. <a href=\"http://www.vivathemes.com/\">Viva Themes</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www