\">UpThemes</a></span></li></ul><p>All of the polls and instructions can be found just after the jump, so be sure to click through to have your voice heard. Voting will take place for the next 48 hours, and close at midnight on the 12th (Eastern Standard Time).</p><p>If you need a reminder, the rules can be found <a title=\"How to win your Theme Madness 2011 Trophy\" href=\"http://wpcandy.com/announces/theme-madness-2011-rules\">here</a>. Good luck to everyone playing!</p><p><span id=\"more-16735\"></span></p><h3>WooThemes vs. Themeopoly</h3><p><a name=\"pd_a_4872663\"></a><div class=\"PDS_Poll\" id=\"PDI_container4872663\"></div><p><br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/poll/4872663/\">View This Poll</a><br /><br /><span><a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/features-surveys/\">survey software</a></span><br /> </p><p>Remember, along with this poll you can also vote two other ways:</p><ul><li><span><strong>The away game:</strong> Tweet your vote using the <a title=\"#wpmadness hashtag on Twitter\" href=\"http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23wpmadness\">#wpmadness</a> hashtag and mention either <a title=\"WooThemes on Twitter\" href=\"http://twitter.com/woothemes\">@WooThemes</a> or <a title=\"Themeopoly\" href=\"http://twitter.com/themeopoly\">@Themeopoly</a>.</span></li><li><span><strong>The home game:</strong> If either WooThemes or Themeopoly start up a post on their blog, your comment there will count as a vote as well.</span></li></ul><h3>Theme Team vs. AppThemes</h3><p><a name=\"pd_a_4872713\"></a><div class=\"PDS_Poll\" id=\"PDI_container4872713\"></div><p><br /> <br /> <a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/poll/4872713/\">View This Poll</a><br /><br /><span><a href=\"http://polldaddy.com/features-surveys/\">survey software</a></span><br /> </p><p>Remember, along with this poll you can also vote two other ways:</p><ul><li><strong>The away game:</strong> Tweet your vote using the <a title=\"#wpmadness hashtag on Twitter\" href=\"http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23