osts to function. Choose whether to display author bios, related posts and more.\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"intro\";}i:18;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:15:\"Respond Caption\";s:4:\"desc\";s:56:\"This snippet will display near the comment respond form.\";s:2:\"id\";s:18:\"tz_respond_caption\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";}i:19;a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:16:\"Homepage Options\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"heading\";}i:20;a:3:{s:4:\"name\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"message\";s:106:\"Setup the display of your homepage. Choose to enable the Magic Door and which item to open upon page load.\";s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"intro\";}i:21;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:21:\"Enable the Magic Door\";s:4:\"desc\";s:119:\"Check this to enable the usage of the magic door. If disabled, the portfolio items will link to their respective pages.\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"tz_magic_door\";s:3:\"std\";s:5:\"false\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"checkbox\";}i:22;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:27:\"Portfolio Post to Open With\";s:4:\"desc\";s:155:\"Input the ID of the portfolio post you wish to open the door with, if left empty the door will be closed. This will only work if the Magic door is enabled.\";s:2:\"id\";s:19:\"tz_magic_door_state\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";}}', 'yes'),
